A WOMAN and young child have been found murdered in bushes near Thambo Street Atlantis, Western Cape.They were found on Tuesday.The motive for the murders is unknown and no arrests have been made, Lieutenant-Colonel Andr&egrave; Traut said.The 22-year-old woman is believed to be the mother of the 2-year-old child, News24 has reliably learnt.Their heads had been covered with sand. The mother was lying in a pool of her own blood, sources said. http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/mom-and-her-2-year-old-child-found-murdered-in-atlantis-20170607